      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a simple fixer-upper? This vehicle is ready for some TLC! While it shows significant wear and will need some mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a great opportunity for anyone handy with a wrench to get on the road affordably. Grab a bargain and make it your own!",
