      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. The exterior finish is flawless, with a deep luster and no imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition. Every component functions perfectly, and the car has been meticulously maintained to preserve its original quality. A buyer can expect a vehicle that is essentially brand new in every measurable way.",
