      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that can only be described as showroom-perfect. Every aspect of this motorcar, from its pristine exterior finish to its flawless interior appointments, reflects a history of fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. This represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire an investment-grade example that delivers an unparalleled driving experience. Inspection will reveal a vehicle that remains indistinguishable from new.",
